StoxLandingDataExample.Rd

Example of data formatted as StoxLandingData, with some additional columns added with AddGearGroupStoxLanding, AddStratumStoxLanding, and AddAreaPositionStoxLanding, and AddStratumStoxLanding, and AddPeriodStoxLanding. The data contain saithe landings by Norwegian vessels in areas (mainareaFdir2018) "00", "03", "04", "05","06", in 2021.

Usage

data(StoxLandingDataExample)

Format

StoxLandingData

Examples

 RstoxFDA::plotBubbleMap(RstoxFDA::StoxLandingDataExample$Landing, 
      "Area", "RoundWeight", RstoxFDA::mainareaFdir2018)
